Cell["\<\
In odd dimension the Weyl decomposition does not exist; ToWeylBasis emits \
ToWeylBasis::oddDim and returns the Dirac basis instead. The captured message \
text is shown below; the function still returns a usable list of matrices:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->678380918,ExpressionUUID->"6ea574e5-1a29-4b3e-9466-86e920439d48"],

